0we%20headed%20to%20the%20party%2C%20which%20was%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border.%20I%20had%20been%20there%20once%20before%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20good%20time.%20We%20arrived%20at%20around%205%20am%2C%20and%20we%20were%20immediately%20greeted%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20music.%20We%20grabbed%20a%20drink%20and%20started%20to%20dance.%20At%20around%206%3A20%20am%2C%20we%20went%20back%20to%20the%20bar%20to%20get%20another%20drink.%20Suddenly%2C%20someone%20started%20yelling%20at%20what%20seemed%20like%20rockets%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20understand%20what%20was%20happening%20at%20first%2C%20but%20then%20I%20saw%20it.%20Missiles%20were%20being%20fired%20from%20Gaza%20towards%20us.%20The%20sky%20was%20exploding%2C%20and%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20was%20shooting%20back.%20At%206%3A31%20am%2C%20the%20music%20stopped%20at%20the%20party%2C%20and%20people%20started%20to%20panic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supernova%20Sukkot%20Gathering%2C%20a%20weekend-long%20outdoor%20trance%20music%20festival%2C%20is%20held%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20Sukkot%20festival%2C%20and%20continues%20well%20into%20the%20morning%20in%20Re'im%2C%20a%20village%20approximately%205%20km%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Chase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20running%20for%20our%20lives.%20The%20terrorists%20were%20shooting%20at%20us%20from%20all%20directions.%20We%20saw%20smashed%20cars%20full%20of%20bullet%20holes%2C%20and%20wounded%20people%20bleeding.%20Ambulances%20were%20trying%20to%20reach%20them%2C%20but%20they%20were%20being%20shot%20at%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sharvit%20said.%20%26quot%3BMe%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20and%20two%20of%20our%20friends%20ran%20all%20over%20the%20area.%20We%20didn't%20know%20where%20we%20were%20going%2C%20but%20we%20just%20kept%20running.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Sharvit%20and%20her%20husband%2C%2024%2C%20have%20a%20baby%20boy%2C%20just%20one%20and%20a%20half%20months%20old%2C%