26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20said%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20explained%20the%20party's%20position%20on%20X%20just%20a%20day%20earlier%20and%20referred%20to%20both%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20and%20the%20Palestine%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20facing%20an%20internal%20revolt%20after%20the%20declaration%20of%20poll%20candidates'%20names%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20distract%20people%20from%20this%20internal%20rift%20and%20raising%20such%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20(BJP%20leader)%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiaji%20that%20he%20should%20remember%20Vajpayeeji's%20speech%20and%20analyse%20what%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20only%20talking%20about%20the%20Congress%20and%20has%20forgotten%20its%20own%20history%20as%20well%20as%20Vajpayeeji's%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20general%20secretary%20Mr%20Vijayvargia%20had%2C%20in%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BExtremely%20condemnable.%20CWC%20has%20passed%20a%20resolution%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine%20regarding%20the%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20once%20again%20passed%20a%20resolution%20taking%20a%20decision%20against%20national%20policy%20and%20national%20interest.%20How%20low%20will%20the%20Congress%20stoop%20to%20to%20please%20the%20people%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%3F%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20ready%20to%20compromise%20with%20terrorism%20also.%20We%20and%20our%20party%20have%20also%20been%20in%20the%20opposition%20but%20never%20took%20any%20step%20against%20national%20interest.%20The%20Congress's%20hand%20is%20with%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijayvargia%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20opposition