20Coach%20Issues%20Major%20Update%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20men's%20cricket%20team%20batting%20coach%20Vikram%20Rathour%20disclosed%20that%20Shubman%20Gill%20was%20hospitalized%20but%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bprecaution%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20hotel%20in%20Chennai.%20Gill%20has%20been%20battling%20an%20illness%20and%20is%20still%20in%20the%20recovery%20stage%20in%20Chennai.%20The%20young%20opening%20batter%20missed%20India's%20opening%20match%20against%20Australia%20in%20Chennai.%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20on%20Monday%20ruled%20out%20Gill%20from%20India's%20clash%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%20Delhi%20after%20confirming%20that%20he%20stayed%20in%20Chennai%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20medical%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERathour%20was%20quizzed%20about%20an%20update%20on%20Gill%20while%20referring%20to%20a%20news%20item%20that%20he%20was%20hospitalised%20and%20then%20he%20has%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERathour%20shed%20some%20light%20on%20the%20matter%20and%20said%20in%20the%20pre-match%20press%20conference%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20recovering%20well.%20He%20was%20hospitalised%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20that%20was%20more%20as%20a%20precaution.%20He%20is%20back%20in%20the%20hotel%3B%20he%20is%20recovering%20well.%20So%2C%20being%20monitored%20by%20the%20medical%20team%20and%20whatever%20update%20we%20get%2C%20we%20are%20hoping%20that%20he%20will%20recover%20pretty%20soon.%20He%20is%20looking%20good%20actually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Gill's%20absence%2C%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20same%20playing%20XI%20that%20they%20named%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20campaign%20opener%20against%20Australia.%20Ishan%20Kishan%20will%20be%20the%20most%20viable%20option%20to%20open%20alongside%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERathour%20stressed%20India's%20experienced%20batting%20unit%20and%20asserted%20that%20batters%20know%20how%20to%20play%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20even%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20freedom%20they%20are%20enjoying%20in%20their%20respective%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20very%20experienced%20batting%20unit%20at%20the%20moment.%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20message%20is%20required.%20Everyone%20knows%20how%20they%20have%20to%20play%20in%20this%20format.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20settled%20batting%20unit%20at%20the%20moment.%20Everyone%20has%20their%20own%20way.%20We%20are%20giving%20them%20the%20freedom%20to%20play%20the%20way%20they%20want%20to%20play.%20And%20we%20understand%20that%20everybody%20has%20a%20different%20way%20of%20playing.%20But%20everyone%20has%20their%20own%20way%20of%20playing%20and%20we%20have%20the%20trust%20that%20if%20they%20play%20and%20back%20themselves%2C%20we%20will%20achieve%20what%20we%20are%20looking%20to%20achieve%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathour%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20face%20Afghanistan%20in%20their%20second%20World%20Cup%20clash%20at%20the%20Arun%20Jaitley%20Stadium%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696993620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F3f6mdes8_shubman-gill-afp_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fshubman-gill-was-hospitalised-but-indias-batting-coach-issues-major-update-4469080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vikram%20Rathour%20was%20quizzed%20about%20an%20update%20on%20Gill%20while%20referring%20to%20a%20news%20item%20that%20he%20was%20hospitalised%20and%20then%20he%20has%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20hotel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fshubman-gill-was-hospitalised-but-in