%26quot%3BSuperbug%26quot%3B%20Bacteria%3A%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20Loma%20Linda%20University%20in%20a%20recent%20study%20said%20that%20your%20local%20fast-food%20soda%20fountain%20may%20be%20contaminated%20with%20coliform%20bacteria%2C%20an%20indicator%20of%20water%20impurity.%20The%20study%20further%20said%20that%20the%20water%20was%20contaminated%20with%20the%20deadliest%20%26quot%3Bsuperbug%26quot%3B%20germs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuperbug%20germs%20including%20antibiotic-resistant%20Pseudomonas%20aeruginosa%20and%20Campylobacter%20jejuni%2C%20as%20well%20as%20listeria%2C%20salmonella%20and%20E.%20coli%20were%20found%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F10%2F10%2Fdeadly-superbug-bacteria-detected-in-soda-fountains-study%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20published%20in%20August%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiwaponline.com%2Fws%2Farticle%2F23%2F9%2F3578%2F96866%2FMicrobial-contamination-analysis-of-drinking-water%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDrinking%20Water%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20claims%20that%20these%20disease-causing%20germs%20were%20found%20in%20almost%20half%20of%20soda%20fountains.%20They%20also%20found%20germs%20in%2080%20%25%20of%20swabs%20from%20the%20taps%20of%20soda%20fountains%2050%20%25%20of%20restaurant%20tap%20water%20and%2020%20%25%20of%20water-vending%20machines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20calls%20into%20question%20the%20sanitation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20water%20from%20soda%20fountains%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20government%20and%20manufacturer%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20say%20that%20soda%20fountain%20contamination%20is%20only%20in%20the%20eastern%20Coachella%20Valley%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20Hile%2C%20a%20researcher%20affiliated%20with%20Loma%20Linda%20and%20the%20study's%20lead%20author%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2