%20conflicting%20counts%20of%20the%20number%20of%20dead%20and%20injured%20from%20the%20previous%20earthquakes%2C%20but%20the%20disaster%20ministry%20has%20said%202%2C053%20people%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20give%20exact%20numbers%20for%20dead%20and%20wounded%20as%20it%20is%20in%20flux%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20disaster%20management%20ministry%20spokesman%20Mullah%20Janan%20Sayeq.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20immediate%20reports%20of%20new%20casualties%20after%20Wednesday's%20quake%2C%20which%20hit%20near%20Herat%20city%2C%20home%20to%20more%20than%20half%20a%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20earthquakes%20completely%20destroyed%20at%20least%2011%20villages%20in%20Herat%20province's%20Zenda%20Jan%20district%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20single%20house%20is%20left%2C%20not%20even%20a%20room%20where%20we%20could%20stay%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2040-year-old%20Mohammad%20Naeem%2C%20who%20told%20AFP%20he%20lost%2012%20relatives%2C%20including%20his%20mother%2C%20after%20Saturday's%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20live%20here%20anymore.%20You%20can%20see%2C%20our%20family%20got%20martyred%20here.%20How%20could%20we%20live%20here%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20reported%20that%20many%20Herat%20residents%20had%20been%20spending%20their%20nights%20living%20in%20tents%20in%20the%20open%20air%20due%20to%20a%20fear%20of%20aftershocks%20following%20the%20weekend%20tremors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProviding%20shelter%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20will%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20Afghanistan's%20Taliban%20authorities%2C%20who%20seized%20power%20in%20August%202021%2C%20and%20have%20fractious%20relations%20with%20international%20aid%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20is%20frequently%20hit%20by%20deadly%20earthquakes%2C%20but%20the%20weekend%20disaster%20was%20the%20worst%20to%20strike%20the%20war-ravaged%20country%20in%20more%20than%2025%2