Cem%3E%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20sales%20director%20at%20a%20software-as-a-service%20company%20in%20Singapore%20who%20landed%20her%20first%20job%2C%20at%20Uber%2C%20after%20tweeting%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInsider%20verified%20Wee's%20account%20with%20her%20then-supervisor%20at%20Uber.%20Uber%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%2025-year-old%20fresh%20graduate%20in%20communications%2C%20I%20was%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elooking%20for%20my%20first%20job.%20That's%20when%20I%20tweeted%20at%20Uber%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20%40uber%20rating%20is%20higher%20than%20my%20GPA.%20Can%20I%20put%20this%20on%20my%20CV%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Cherylyn%20Wee's%20tweet%20at%20Uber%20in%202017%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651fea626e038039826b4b42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221226%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20Wee's%20tweet%20at%20Uber%20in%202017.%3Cp%3ECherylyn%20Wee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20my%20GPA%20was%20a%204%20out%20of%205.%20And%20my%20Uber%20rating%20was%204.9%20out%20of%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20mock%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20with%20my%20tweet%2C%20imagining%20in%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20way%20that%20I%20was%20already%20working%20for%20Uber%20by%20being%20a%20passenger%2C%20with%20responsibilities%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ERegularly%20assessing%20the%20efficiency%20and%20quality%20of%20the%20Singapore%20network%20of%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20an%20advocate%20for%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAssisting%20in%20the%20external%20communication%20of%20Uber%20to%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20tweet%20got%20the%20company's%20attention%2C%20and%20Uber%20invited%20me%20to%20apply%20for%20roles%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20role%20I%20applied%20for%20didn't%20pan%20out.%20But%20someone%20else%20at%20Uber%20saw%20my%20tweet%2C%20and%20they%20reached%20out%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20different%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20how%20a%20tweet%20helped%20me%20land%20my%20first%20job%2C%20as%20a%20marketing%20coordinator%20at%20Uber%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20constantly%20online%20can%20pay%20off%20in%20unexpected%20ways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20I%20was%20really%20active%20on%20Twitter%20(now%20X)%20and%20constantly%20engaging%20with%20brands%20I%20encountered%20in%20my%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20typo%20in%20a%20restaurant's%20promotion%20material%2C%20and%20I%20tweeted%20at%20them%3A%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I've%20found%20a%20typo%20in%20your%20content%2C%20could%20I%20get%20a%20bag%20of%20free%20popcorn%20the%20next%20time%20I%20come%20by%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Uber%20came%20to%20Singapore%2C%20I%20figured%20that%20I%20should%20send%20something%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20saw%20that%20the%20ride-hailing%20company%20had%20a%20passenger%20rating%2C%20I%20thought%3A%20Oh%2C%20my%20god%2C%20am%20I%20a%20good%20passenger%3F%20I%20had%20a%204.9%20out%20of%205%20rating%2C%20so%20I%20guess%20that's%20a%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20next%20thought%20was%3A%20How%20can%20I%20add%20this%20to%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20I%20couldn't%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20it%20might%20be%20funny%20if%20I%20could%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20that%20might%20help%20me%20stand%20out%2C%20especially%20because%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20role%20in%20marketing.%20And%20that's%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20tweeting%20came%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20intentional%20with%20what%20you%20write%20online%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cherlyn%20Wee%20on%20her%20last%20day%20at%20Uber%2C%20which%20was%20also%20the%20day%20that%20Uber%20exited%20Singapore%20in%202018%20after%20selling%20off%20its%20operations%20to%20a%20local%20company.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651fec5d6e038039826b4e1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22858%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWee%20on%20her%20last%20day%20at%20the%20Uber%20Singapore%20office%20in%202018%2C%20which%20was%20also%20the%20day%20Uber%20exited%20the%20country.%3Cp%3ECherylyn%20Wee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20Uber%20after%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20when%20the%20company%20exited%20Singapore%20%E2%80%94%20but%20working%20there%20was%20eye-opening%20because%20of%20its%20startup%20mentality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20feel%20a%20little%20weird%20switching%20from%20being%20the%20person%20tweeting%20at%20Uber%20to%20becoming%20somewhat%20responsible%20for%20what%20went%20up%20on%20Uber%20Singapore's%20social-media%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20few%20roles%20I%20applied%20for%2C%20many%20employers%20looked%20at%20my%20LinkedIn%20profile.%20And%20because%20I%20had%20written%20about%20the%20whole%20experience%20of%20landing%20my%20first%20job%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20tweet%2C%20these%20employers%20would%20reference%20it%20in%20our%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20appreciated%20the%20creativity%20and%20that%20it%20landed%20me%20a%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20I've%20caught%20up%20with%20years%20later%20still%20say%20to%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20you're%20that%20Uber%20girl%20who%20got%20the%20job%20because%20of%20that%20tweet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdeas%20are%20great%2C%20but%20it's%20all%20about%20follow-through%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%20have%20for%20people%20who%20are%20job%20h