0side%20of%20the%20resistance%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDarmanin%20said%20he%20had%20made%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20reports%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20courts%20about%20similar%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Elisabeth%20Borne%20stressed%20that%20France%20will%20not%20tolerate%20%26quot%3Bany%20anti-Semitic%20act%20or%20comment%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20pro-Palestinian%20demonstrations%20due%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Paris%20on%20Thursday%20have%20been%20banned%2C%20Paris%20police%20chief%20Laurent%20Nunez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20ban%20was%20imposed%20%26quot%3Bin%20view%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20disturbing%20public%20order%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorne%20promised%20%26quot%3Bthe%20utmost%20firmness%20to%20all%20those%20who%20would%20use%20this%20conflict%20as%20a%20pretext%20for%20anti-Semitism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20Jewish%20community%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20with%20you.%20To%20attack%20you%20is%20to%20attack%20the%20whole%20Republic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%2050%20%26quot%3Banti-Semitic%20acts%26quot%3B%2C%20some%20of%20them%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20serious%26quot%3B%2C%20have%20been%20recorded%20in%20France%20since%20Saturday's%20attack%20on%20Israel%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Darmanin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20going%20in%20front%20of%20synagogues%2C%20lots%20of%20them%2C%20shouting%20threats.%20There%20have%20been%2016%20arrests%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days.%20Drones%20flying%20into%20schoolyards%20with%20cameras.%20But%20also%20slogans%2C%20tags%2C%20threatening%20letters%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20interior%20minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20police%20services%20had%20noted%20%26quot%3B1%2C000%20anti-Semitic%20reports%20in%2048%20hours%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%20France%20also%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20it%20is%20opposed%20to%20suspending%20aid%20that%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%26quot%3B%20ben