of%20their%20own%20troops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20intelligence%20that%20Israel%20is%20able%20to%20collect%20before%20any%20invasion%20would%20come%20into%20play%20as%20ground%20troops%20moved%20in.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20after%20the%20potential%20assault%20begins%2C%20every%20individual%20soldier%20and%20vehicle%20becomes%20an%20intelligence%20sensor%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20communicate%20intelligence%20in%20both%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20that%20granular%20tactical%20operator%26quot%3B%20and%20making%20sure%20%26quot%3Btheir%20observations%20feed%20back%20into%20a%20collective%20picture%20accurately%20so%20that%20the%20maneuver%20commanders%20can%20do%20things%20like%20prevent%20unnecessary%20loss%20of%20civilian%20life%20and%20get%20a%20better%2C%20more%20accurate%20picture%20of%20where%20hazards%20may%20exist%20for%20sabotage%20or%20for%20ambush%26quot%3B%20is%20crucial%2C%20Borene%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20rises%20following%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20on%20October%2010%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525c2f168f1d46f52add515%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20rises%20following%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20on%20October%2010%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Momen%20Faiz%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20any%20potential%20battlespace%2C%20Israel%20has%20significantly%20more%20firepower%20than%20the%20Iran-backed%20Hamas%2C%C2%A0but%20the%20latter%20still%20poses%20a%20threat.%20It's%20unclear%20how%20much%20capability%20the%20militant%20group%20lost%20during%20its%20initial%20attacks%20%E2%80%94%20as%20many%20as%201%2C500%20Palestinian%20militants%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fhamas-770-dead-in-gaza-4000-wounde