20phone%20call%20with%20his%20Israeli%20counterpart%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20to%20discuss%20the%20escalation%20in%20violence%20in%20West%20Asia%20since%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fatalities%20have%20kept%20mounting%20in%20the%20fighting%2C%20with%20at%20least%20900%20Israelis%20killed%20after%20hundreds%20of%20Hamas%20militants%20crossed%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20border%20and%20missiles%20hit%20Israeli%20cities.%20In%20response%2C%20Israeli%20counterattacks%20have%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20830%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20there%20is%20growing%20concern%20about%20a%20potential%20Israeli%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20sole%20official%20response%20had%20been%20made%20by%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%20afternoon%20when%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eexpressed%20%E2%80%9Csolidarity%20with%20Israel%E2%80%9D%20through%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1710614655620534296%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehis%20official%20account%20on%20X%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20days%20later%2C%20Modi%20reiterated%20the%20sentiment%20when%20Netanyahu%20called%20him%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20expressed%20deep%20condolences%20and%20sympathy%20for%20those%20killed%20and%20wounded%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20and%20conveyed%20that%20people%20of%20India%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20in%20this%20difficult%20hour%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20Indian%20government%20readout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20thank%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnetanyahu%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40netanyahu%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20phone%20call%20and%20providi