20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20like%20Brazil%2C%20China%20and%20Indonesia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJapan%2C%20was%20perhaps%20the%20only%20G-7%20member%2C%20which%20not%20only%20condemned%20the%20attack%20but%20also%20called%20on%20all%20parties%20%E2%80%9Cto%20exercise%20maximum%20restrain%E2%80%9D.%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkishida230%2Fstatus%2F1710912119330517151%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFumio%20Kishida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20Tokyo%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20concerned%20about%20a%20number%20of%20casualties%20in%20Gaza%20as%20well%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20India%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20had%20clear%20bipartisan%20support%2C%20there%20are%20sharper%20differences%20among%20Indian%20political%20parties%20in%20their%20initial%20reaction%20to%20the%20escalating%20violence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress%20party%20had%20specifically%20referred%20to%20the%20need%20for%20violence%20to%20stop%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Clegitimate%20aspirations%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20The%20ruling%20BJP%20had%20accused%20Congress%20of%20playing%20%E2%80%9Cvote%20bank%20politics%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20official%20position%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FPortal%2FForeignRelation%2FIndia-Palestine_Bilateral_Relations.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublic%20brief%20by%20MEA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20has%20been%20that%20it%20supports%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnegotiated%20solution%20resulting%20in%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%2C%20viable%20and%20united%20State%20of%20Palestine%2C%20within%20secure%20and%20recognised%20borders%2C%20at%20peace%20beside%20Israel%20as%20endorsed%20in%20the%20relevant%20UNSC%20and%20UNGA%20Resolu