n%20to%20broker%3F%20Is%20it%20dead%20in%20the%20water%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20only%20paused%20for%20a%20short%20duration%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E8)%20Very%20predictably%20the%20American%20government%20has%20announced%20its%20rock-solid%20unwavering%20support%20for%20Israel%20and%20Biden%20has%20rushed%20the%20US%20aircraft%20carrier%20Gerald%20Ford%20and%20other%20ships%20into%20the%20area%20presumably%20in%20a%20message%20to%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah%20to%20exercise%20restraint.%20Is%20there%20a%20limit%20to%20how%20far%20Washington%20can%20go%20without%20adversely%20affecting%20its%20relationship%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%3F%20After%20all%2C%20they%20are%20majority%20Muslim%20nations%20where%20public%20sentiment%20is%20not%20with%20Israel%20and%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20like%20this%20display%20of%20American%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E9)%20Now%20other%20than%20Israel%2C%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20nearest%20neighbour%20is%20Egypt.%20But%20Egypt%20was%20also%20the%20first%20Arab%20country%20to%20recognise%20Israel%20almost%2045%20years%20ago.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20policy%20that%E2%80%99s%20popular%20with%20the%20Egyptian%20people%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20Israeli%20terrorists%20in%20Alexandria%20has%20underlined%20that.%20How%20do%20you%20see%20Egypt%20handling%20this%20crisis%20on%20its%20borders%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E10)%20Finally%2C%20what%20impact%20will%20this%20have%20on%20Ukraine%3F%20So%20far%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20the%20single%20focus%20of%20American%20and%20Western%20concern.%20That%20clearly%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20So%20has%20the%20Hamas-Israel%20crisis%20diminished%20the%20importance%20of%20Ukraine%20or%2C%20at%20least%2C%20reduced%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20and%20resources%20Washington%20can%20give%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E11)%20One%20last%20question%3A%20How%20do%20you%20read%20the%20response%20from%20Beijing%20and%20Moscow%3F%20Beijing%20has%20called%20for%20de-escalation%20and%2