0be%20hit%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDecarbonisation%20%E2%80%93%20reducing%20the%20carbon%20emissions%20produced%20by%20human%20activities%20such%20as%20the%20burning%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20%E2%80%93%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20techniques%20advocated%20to%20keep%20global%20warming%20below%20specific%20levels%20so%20as%20to%20reduce%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%20(such%20as%20heat%20waves%2C%20intense%20rainfall%20and%20other%20extreme%20weather%20events)%20worldwide.%20One%20means%20of%20decarbonisation%20is%20to%20shift%20to%20cleaner%20forms%20of%20energy%2C%20such%20as%20solar%20and%20wind%20power%2C%20and%20decrease%20coal%20production%20by%20shutting%20down%20existing%20mines.%20But%20what%20of%20the%20coal%20mines%20that%20have%20to%20close%20down%3F%20The%20coal%20industry%20is%20a%20crucial%20source%20of%20livelihood%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas%20in%20developing%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Global%20Energy%20Monitor%2C%20a%20US-based%20NGO%20that%20compiles%20and%20publishes%20information%20on%20clean%20energy%20worldwide%20%E2%80%93%20including%20transitioning%20to%20such%20energy%20sources%2C%20compiled%20data%20on%20employment%20at%204%2C300%20active%20and%20proposed%20coal%20mines%20and%20projects%20around%20the%20world%20that%20are%20cumulatively%20responsible%20for%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20global%20coal%20production.%20This%20was%20done%20through%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalenergymonitor.org%2Fprojects%2Fglobal-coal-mine-tracker%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20Coal%20Mine%20Tracker%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20analysis%20included%20data%20from%20mines%20in%2070%20countries%2C%20including%20India%2C%20which%20has%20an%20estimated%203.3%20lakh%20workers%20in%20coal%20mines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20finds%20that%20nearly%2027%20lakh%20coal%20miners%20produce%2093%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20coal%2C%20with%20the%20vast%20majority%20working%20in%20Asia%20(around%2022%20lakh%20jobs).%20By%202050%2C%20around%209.9%20lakh%20coal%20mine%20jobs%20will%20no%20longer%20exist%20due%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20mines%20across%20the%20world.%20Over%20one-third%20of%20the%20existing%20workforce%20will%20face%20layoffs%2C%20even%20without%20climate%20pledges%20or%20policies%20to%20phase%20out%20coal.%20Currently%2C%204%2C14%2C200%20workers%20operate%20mines%20that%20may%20reach%20their%20end%20of%20operation%20before%202035.%20So%20the%20layoffs%20by%202035%20will%20affect%20on%20average%20100%20workers%20per%20day%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20them%20are%20in%20Asia%20alone.%20The%20Global%20Energy%20Monitor%20report%20estimates%20that%20China%20and%20India%20will%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20layoffs%20as%20coal%20mines%20are%20closed%20down.%20China%20has%20more%20than%201.5%20million%20coal%20miners%20who%20produce%20over%2085%25%20of%20its%20coal%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20half%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20output.%20India%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20coal%20producer%20after%20China%20and%20the%20state-owned%20Coal%20India%20will%20face%20the%20most%20potential%20layoffs%20by%202050%3A%20an%20estimated%2073%2C800%20direct%20workers%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20finds%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20mines%20expected%20to%20close%20in%20the%20coming%20decades%20have%20no%20planning%20underway%20to%20extend%20the%20life%20of%20those%20operations%20or%20manage%20a%20transition%20to%20a%20post-coal%20economy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F182619562_00d6f703b6_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20coal%20mine%20at%20an%20unspecified%20location%20in%20India.%20Credit%3A%20Nitin%20Kirloskar%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F182619562_00d6f703b6_b.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F182619562_00d6f703b6_b-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-9811%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20coal%20mine%20at%20an%20unspecified%20location%20in%20India.%20Photo%3A%20Nitin%20Kirloskar%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Regional%20balances%20are%20crucial%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20coal%20industry%20has%20a%20long%20list%20of%20mines%20that%20will%20close%20in%20the%20near%20term%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20them%20state-owned%20enterprises%20with%20a%20government%20stake%2C%E2%80%9D%20commented%20researcher%20Tiffany%20Means%2C%20one%20of%20the%20co-authors%20of%20the%20Global%20Energy%20Monitor%20report.%20%E2%80%9CGovernments%20need%20to%20shoulder%20their%20share%20of%20the%20burden%20to%20ensure%20a%20managed%20transition%20for%20those%20workers%20and%20communities%20as%20we%20move%20into%20a%20clean%20energy%20economy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%E2%80%9Cjust%E2%80%9D%20transition%20involves%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20ensuring%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20workers%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20jobs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilo.org%2Fglobal%2Ftopics%2Fgreen-jobs%2FWCMS_824102%2Flang--en%2Findex.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520Just%2520Transition%2520involves%2520maximizing%2Cfundamental%2520labour%2520principles%2520and%2520rights%2520.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organisation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20just%20transition%20is%20about%20%E2%80%9Cgreening%20the%20economy%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20as%20fair%20and%20inclusive%20as%20possible%20to%20everyone%20concerned%2C%20creating%20decent%20work%20opportunities%20and%20leaving%20no%20one%20behind%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Findia-just-transition-plans-coal%2F%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Oldest%20Coal%20Belt%20Shows%20Why%20Plans%20for%20Transition%20Must%20Begin%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20wakeup%20call%20to%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20problem%20at%20hand%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Runa%20Sarkar%2C%20professor%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Calcutta.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coal%20mining%20region%20most%20affected%20by%20mine%20closure%20is%20West%20Bengal%20in%20India.%20Further%2C%20for%20every%20worker%20affected%20in%20the%20formal%20economy%2C%20at%20least%20four%20others%20are%20affected%20in%20the%20informal%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sarkar%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20however%2C%20coal%20production%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20talks%20of%20reopening%20some%20closed%20mines%20to%20meet%20current%20demand%2C%20she%20added.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20October%202022%20also%20issued%20fresh%20guidelines%20on%20mine%20closure%20taking%20into%20account%20its%20associated%20ecological%20and%20socioeconomic%20complexities%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20around%20building%20a%20circular%20economy%20around%20coal%20which%20recognises%20that%20a%20coal%20mining%20township%20soon%20becomes%20about%20much%20more%20than%20about%20coal%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20commented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20one%20must%20take%20into%20account%20that%20areas%20which%20are%20rich%20in%20coal%20are%20not%20the%20ones%20where%20the%20sun%20shines%20or%20the%20wind%20blows%20in%20abundance%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20implies%20a%20widening%20of%20regional%20imbalances%20as%20a%20result%20of%20mine%20closures.%20All%20this%20necessitates%20a%20more%20broad-based%20bottom-up%20discussion%20around%20energy%20transition%20to%20ensure%20one%20which%20is%20both%20regionally%20balanced%2C%20sustainable%20and%20just.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696951767000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F11124719%2Fezgif.com-gif-maker-9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Fcoal-india-could-layoff-70000-workers-2050-just-transition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20shows%20that%20a%20just%20and%20sustainable%20transition%20to%20clean%20energy%20will%20be%20crucial%2C%20especially%20for%20specific%20regions%20in%20the%20country%20that%20depend%20heavily%20on%20coal-based%20jobs%2C%20said%20experts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Fcoal-india-could-layoff-70000-workers-2050-just-transition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Luminescent'%20horseshoe%20crab%20picture%20wins%20biologist%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696951740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-laurent-ballesta-wildlife-photographer_6316655.jpg%3F20231010125723%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbiologist-wins-wildlife-photographer-of-the-year-for-a-second-time-12981830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20%26quot%3Bluminescent%26quot%3B%20picture%20of%20a%20tri-spine%20horseshoe%20crab%20gliding%20along%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20sea%20has%20won%20Frenchman%20Laurent%20Ballesta%20his%20second%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year%20title.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbiologist-wins-wildlife-photographer-of-the-year-for-a-second-time-12981830%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbiologist-wins-wildlife-photographer-of-the-year-for-a-second-time-12981830%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbiologist-wins-wildlife-photographer-of-the-year-for-a-second-time-12981830%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drone%20captures%20flock%20of%20sheep%20crossing%20US%20highway%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696950756000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F140E4%2Fproduction%2F_131384128_p0gkms00.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67070505%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Timelapse%20footage%20shows%20the%20animals%20moving%20like%20a%20murmuration%20of%20birds%20near%20the%20city%20of%20Othello%2C%20in%20Washington%20state%2C%20USA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-67070505%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delimitation%20Should%20Not%20Solely%20Be%20Determined%20by%20Numerical%20Superiority%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%20Chelameswar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10192713%2FScreenshot-2023-10-10-at-7.26.25%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERetired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Jasti%20Chelameswar%20asked%20whether%20there%20should%20be%20a%20pattern%20where%20somebody%20gets%20a%20premium%20for%20their%20nonperformance%2C%20with%20the%20South%20Indian%20states%20paying%20for%20the%20nonperforming%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20%E2%80%9CDelimitation%3A%20Southern%20Discomfort%20And%20Solutions%E2%80%9D%20at%20Dakshin%20Dialogues%202023%2C%20the%20annual%20flagship%20thought%20conclave%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Saturday%2C%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20matter%20of%20delimitation%20and%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Vote%E2%80%99%20should%20be%20debated%20seriously.%20Funds%20from%20the%20government%20of%20India%20are%20being%20used%20for%20the%20different%20states%E2%80%A6%20Some%20of%20us%20in%20some%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20are%20not%20being%20cared%20for%20so%20well.%20Something%20is%20required%20to%20be%20done.%20But%20should%20it%20be%20such%20a%20pattern%20that%20somebody%20gets%20a%20premium%20for%20their%20non-performance%3F%20How%20to%20solve%20it%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20which%20should%20be%20discussed%20along%20the%20line%20of%20delimitation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Justice%20Chelameswar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20amending%20the%20constitution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20was%20a%20legal%20document%20that%20deserved%20the%20utmost%20respect%3A%20It%20was%20crucial%20not%20to%20view%20it%20as%20something%20infallible%2C%20but%20rather%20subject%20to%20scrutiny%20and%20adaptation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20aspect%20has%20been%20a%20topic%20of%20discussion%20for%20the%20past%2075%20years%2C%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20when%20questions%20arose%20about%20whether%20the%20constitution%20could%20be%20amended%20by%20parliament%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20in%201973%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20the%20constitution%20could%20be%20amended%20by%20parliament%2C%20with%20the%20limitation%20that%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution%20could%20not%20be%20altered.%20Defining%20what%20constitutes%20this%20%E2%80%98basic%20structure%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20complex%20task%2C%20akin%20to%20traditional%20Indian%20philosophy%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20challenging%20to%20explain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20there%20were%20aspects%20of%20the%20constitution%20that%20might%20benefit%20from%20periodic%20reevaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20may%20have%20been%20suitable%20a%20century%20ago%20may%20require%20reexamination%20through%20rigorous%20and%20intelligent%20debate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20should%20not%20be%20solely%20determined%20by%20shouting%20and%20numerical%20superiority%3B%20it%20demands%20thoughtful%20consideration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWm4g7lQi1zA%3Fsi%3Db1ZfH2T7bbEVDEMK%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20interpreting%20the%20constitution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20framers%20of%20the%20constitution%20were%20individuals%20of%20great%20wisdom%2C%20with%20vast%20experience%20and%20deep%20commitment%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20noted%20the%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20of%20them%20endured%20prolonged%20periods%20of%20incarceration%20during%20the%20British%20colonial%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20sacrifices%20and%20dedication%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development%20and%20democratic%20principles%20culminated%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20this%20constitution%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20are%20aspects%20that%20might%20warrant%20reconsideration.%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20emphasise%20that%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20interpretation%20and%20application%20are%20essential%20for%20its%20relevance%20and%20effectiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20the%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%98one%20person%2C%20one%20vote%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20indeed%20a%20fundamental%20tenet%20of%20democracy.%20However%2C%20it%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20political%20power%2C%20derived%20from%20numerical%20representation%2C%20intersects%20with%20other%20crucial%20aspects%20like%20financial%20distribution.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20an%20economist%2C%20but%20I%20can%20provide%20an%20example%20to%20illustrate%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20there%20are%20two%20high%20courts%20in%20India%20where%20the%20use%20of%20Hindi%20as%20a%20language%20of%20communication%20is%20legally%20permissible%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Other%20states%20have%20subsequently%20joined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20development%20occurred%20in%20the%201950s%20when%20the%20assemblies%20passed%20a%20resolution%2C%20and%20the%20government%20was%20tasked%20with%20notifying%20Hindi%20as%20a%20language%20for%20high%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20this%20decision%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20influenced%20by%20any%20particular%20political%20party.%20However%2C%20despite%20the%20resolution%2C%20the%20use%20of%20Hindi%20in%20high%20courts%20has%20not%20become%20widespread.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20such%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERequest%20for%20Hindi%20in%20court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20once%20attended%20a%20gathering%20where%20the%20demand%20was%20raised%20to%20make%20Hindi%20an%20official%20language%20for%20legal%20documents%20and%20court%20proceedings.%20Many%20speakers%20supported%20this%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20was%20my%20turn%2C%20I%20mentioned%20that%20I%20come%20from%20a%20region%20where%20Hindi%20is%20not%20widely%20spoken%2C%20and%20I%20had%20watched%20numerous%20Hindi%20movies.%20I%20asked%20if%20anyone%20in%20the%20audience%20had%20seen%20even%20one%20South%20Indian%20movie%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20language.%20Surprisingly%2C%20not%20a%20single%20person%20had.%20My%20point%20was%20that%20diversity%20in%20languages%20is%20important%2C%20and%20learning%20more%20languages%20is%20enriching%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%2C%20however%2C%20these%20decisions%20could%20be%20politically%20influenced.%20For%20instance%2C%20Hindi-speaking%20individuals%20formed%20a%20majority%20in%20parliament%2C%20and%20this%20influenced%20decisions%20regarding%20language%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20election%20processes%20should%20adhere%20to%20the%20constitutional%20principle%20that%20the%20ratio%20of%20representation%20among%20states%20should%20be%20roughly%20equitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fdakshin-dialogues%2Fretd-justice-chelameswar-on-delimitation-impact-should-somebody-get-a-premium-for-their-nonperformance%2F%5C%22%3Estory%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20South%20First.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696950042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10192713%2FScreenshot-2023-10-10-at-7.26.25%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelimitation-should-not-solely-be-determined-by-numerical-superiority-former-sc-judge-chelameswar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20debate%20if%20some%20states%20should%20get%20a%20%26quot%3Bpremium%20for%20their%20non-performance%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20retired%20judge%20said%2C%20speaking%20about%20delimitation%20and%20Central%20funds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelimitation-should-not-solely-be-determined-by-numerical-superiority-former-s