rieties%20of%20guava%2C%20pomegranate%2C%20sapodilla%20(%3Cem%3Esapota%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20sweet%20lime%20or%20%3Cem%3Emosambi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Java%20plum%2C%20lemons%2C%20star%20fruit%2C%20avocado%2C%20Singapore%20cherry%20and%20more%2C%20pulses%20such%20as%20pigeon%20pea%20(%3Cem%3Etoor%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20green%20gram%20(%3Cem%3Emoong%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20black%20gram%20(%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Bengal%20gram%20(%3Cem%3Echana%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20legumes%20like%20cowpea%2C%20(lobia)%2C%20peanuts%2C%20and%20the%20oilseed%20sesame%20as%20well%20as%20seasonal%20vegetables%20and%20three%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20rice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20farm%20is%20open%20for%20visitors%20to%20go%20and%20learn%20organic%20farming%20and%20enjoy%20farm%20life.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20farm%20life%20and%20also%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20organic%20compost%20and%20manure%20and%20grow%20their%20own%20food%20naturally%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Alankrutha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20conquering%20the%20food%20and%20clothing%20aspect%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20now%20ready%20to%20move%20on%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98stay%E2%80%99%20part%20of%20their%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-2-1696946570.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20stays%20in%20a%20limestone%20house%20that%20stays%20cool%20during%20the%20summers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-2-1696946570.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-2-1696946570-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-2-1696946570-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F1