EThe%20duo%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20in%20a%20terror%20case%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3Ewhich%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20received%20Chinese%20funding%20to%20criticise%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20promote%20Chinese%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20public%20prosecutor%20(APP)%20Atul%20Srivastava%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20Delhi%20police%20was%20seeking%20judicial%20custody%20because%20their%20physical%20presence%20is%20not%20required%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20Khurana%2C%20opposing%20the%20grant%20of%20judicial%20custody%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbare%20reading%20of%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20FIR%20would%20show%20that%20there%20is%20no%20criminal%20offence%20made%20out%E2%80%9D%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20case%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-case-allegations-uapa-legal-experts%5C%22%3ENewsClick%20Case%3A%20Do%20Allegations%20Justify%20Invoking%20of%20UAPA%3F%20Legal%20Experts%20Weigh%20In.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20allegation%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20used%20any%20bomb%20or%20dynamite%20which%20has%20caused%20loss%20of%20death%20and%20property.%20There%20is%20no%20allegation%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20used%20any%20criminal%20force%20in%20the%20entire%20FIR.%20There%20is%20no%20act%20of%20kidnapping%2C%20detention%20or%20abduction.%20None%20of%20the%20acts%20attributed%20to%20me%20has%20any%20elements%20of%20Section%2015%20of%20UAPA%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhurana%20said%20that%20a%20journalist%20cannot%20be%20punished%20for%20criticising%20the%20government%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsclick-arrests-prabir-purkayastha-amit-chakraborty-remanded-judicial-custody-10-days-delhi-court%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20APP%20Srivastava%20responded%2C%20%E2%80%9CYour%20purpose%20was%20not%20criticising%20(the%20government)%20but%20propagating%20the%20propaganda%20of%20a%20country%20that%20is%20inimical%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhurana%20also%20reiterated%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20not%20received%20any%20money%20from%20China%20and%20all%20investment%20came%20through%20banking%20channels%20and%20was%20duly%20reported%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%2C%20appearing%20for%20NewsClick%E2%80%99s%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakraborty%2C%20said%20his%20client%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR%20as%20an%20accused.%20While%20the%20FIR%20says%20Chakravarti%20owns%20shares%20in%20NewsClick%2C%20his%20holdings%20in%20the%20company%20equal%200.1%25%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20%5Ban%5D%20allegation%20there%20is%20money%20coming%20in%20and%20some%20news%20is%20being%20published%20with%20a%20particular%20agenda.%20I%20have%20not%20been%20involved%20in%20any%20publication.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20journalist%2C%20or%20an%20editor%20or%20writer%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chakravarti%E2%80%99s%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20APP%20Srivastava%20said%20that%20the%20police%20had%20already%20satisfied%20the%20court%20during%20the%20time%20of%20police%20remand%20that%20the%20offences%20were%20made%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20it%20is%20not%20a%20case%20of%20first%20remand.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20first%20remand%2C%20we%20had%20satisfied%20my%20ladyship%20with%20how%20the%20offences%20were%20made%20out%E2%80%A6%20We%20are%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20collecting%20evidence.%20See%20our%20fairness.%20We%20have%20said%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20police%20remand%20as%20of%20now%20and%20will%20ask%20later%20if%20we%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20were%20arrested%20on%20October%203%20and%20were%20remanded%20to%20seven%20days%20of%20police%20custody%20on%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20Monday%20reserved%20its%20order%20in%20the%20pleas%20moved%20by%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-reserves-judgment-on-pleas-challenging-remand-orders-of-newsclick-editor-hr-head%5C%22%3Echallenging%20the%20trial%20court%E2%80%99s%20remand%20order%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696945833000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F10124838%2Fp-house-court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnewsclick-case-purkayasthan-chakravarti-10-days-judicial-custody%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20police%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20was%20seeking%20judicial%20custody%20because%20their%20physical%20presence%20is%20not%20required%20at%20this%20stage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnewsclick-case-purkayasthan-chakravarti-10-days-judicial-custody%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20LG%20Grants%20Sanction%20to%20Prosecute%20Arundhati%20Roy%20in%202010%20'Provocative%20Speeches'%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F15161252%2FArundhati_Roy__Man_Booker_Prize_winner.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EDelhi%20lieutenant%20governor%20V.K.%20Saxena%20has%20accorded%20sanction%20for%20the%20prosecution%20of%20author%20Arundhati%20Roy%20and%20retired%20Kashmir%20professor%20Sheikh%20Showkat%20Hussain%20in%20connection%20with%20a%202010%20case%20accusing%20them%20of%20making%20provocative%20speeches%20that%20called%20for%20separation%20of%20Kashmir%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20note%2C%20Saxena%20has%20noted%20that%20a%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%20is%20made%20out%20against%20Roy%20and%20Hussain%20for%20the%20commission%20of%20offences%20under%20Sections%20153A%2C%20153B%20and%20505%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20for%20their%20speeches%20at%20a%20public%20function%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20While%20Section%20153A%20deals%20with%20offences%20pertaining%20to%20those%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20residence%2C%20Section%20153B%20relates%20to%20offences%20relating%20to%20imputations%2C%20and%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national%20integration.%20Section%20505%20covers%20offences%20relating%20to%20making%20or%20circulation%20of%20false%20statements%2C%20rumours%2C%20or%20information%20with%20a%20specific%20intent%20to%20cause%20mutiny%20or%20fear%20among%20military%20personnel%2C%20inciting%20offences%20against%20the%20state%20or%20public%20tranquility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sanction%20from%20the%20Delhi%20LG%20was%20necessitated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20initiating%20prosecution%20under%20Sections%20153A%20and%20153B%20requires%20prior%20sanction%20from%20the%20government.%20This%20is%20required%20before%20the%20trial%2C%20and%20not%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20the%20preliminary%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20note%20also%20clarifies%20that%20sanction%20has%20not%20been%20provided%20to%20prosecute%20the%20accused%20under%20sedition%20(Section%20124A)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20IPC%20sections%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR.%20However%2C%20a%20case%20under%20the%20section%20is%20made%20out%2C%20the%20note%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20LG%20was%20constrained%20against%20giving%20sanction%20because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-puts-sedition-law-in-abeyance-during-government-review%5C%22%3Elandmark%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20directed%20all%20pending%20trials%2C%20appeals%2C%20and%20proceedings%20with%20respect%20to%20charges%20framed%20under%20sedition%20be%20kept%20in%20abeyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20registered%20on%20November%2029%2C%202010%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20from%20Sushil%20Pandit%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20from%20Kashmir.%20The%20complainant%20said%20speakers%20at%20a%20conference%20organised%20by%20the%20Committee%20for%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners%20(CRPP)%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20%E2%80%98Azadi%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Only%20Way%E2%80%99%20on%20October%2021%2C%202010%20had%20delivered%20%E2%80%9Cprovocative%20speeches%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20also%20called%20for%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cseparation%20of%20Kashmir%20from%20India%E2%80%9D.%20Pandit%20also%20said%20the%20speeches%20were%20provocative%20in%20nature%2C%20thus%20jeopardising%20public%20peace%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20said%20Roy%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9CKashmir%20was%20never%20part%20of%20India%20and%20was%20forcibly%20occupied%20by%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20India%20and%20every%20possible%20effort%20should%20be%20made%20for%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20from%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%93%20Syed%20Ali%20Shah%20Geelani%2C%20a%20Kashmiri%20separatist%20leader%20and%20Syed%20Abdul%20Rahman%20Geelani%2C%20a%20Delhi%20University%20lecturer%20who%20acquitted%20in%20parliament%20attack%20case%20%E2%80%93%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696944911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F15161252%2FArundhati_Roy__Man_Booker_Prize_winner.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lg-grants-sanction-prosecute-arundhati-roy-2010-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20writer-activist%20and%20retired%20professor%20Sheikh%20Showkat%20Hussain%20will%20be%20tried%20for%20promoting%20enmity%20and%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national%20integration.%20Because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20put%20the%20sedition%20law%20in%20abeyance%2C%20the%20LG%20did%20not%20provide%20sanction%20for%20prosecution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lg-grants-sanction-prosecute-arundhati-roy-2010-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Despite%20Repeated%20Requests%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Avoids%20Meeting%20Manipur%20BJP%20MLAs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10171456%2FF8Ee91zbUAA-T1C.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmanipur%2Fbjp-manipur-unit-writes-nadda-public-anger-8962955%2F%5C%22%3Eletter%20recently%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20Manipur%20unit%20to%20party%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20has%20come%20into%20national%20focus%20for%20seeking%20his%20intervention%20to%20%E2%80%9Crevoke%20Article%20355%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20violence-hit%20northeastern%20state%2C%20and%20also%20to%20clarify%20%E2%80%9Cif%20there%20is%20anything%20(Article%20355)%20as%20such%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%20The%20letter%20also%20asks%20that%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20be%20restored%20the%20command%20of%20the%20Unified%20Command%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20anger%20and%20protest%E2%80%9D%20is%20being%20directed%20at%20the%20state%20government%20run%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20needs%20highlighting%20is%20that%20the%20state%20unit%20had%20also%20requested%20Nadda%20%E2%80%9Cto%20persuade%E2%80%9D%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%9Cto%20give%20an%20appointment%20to%20the%20joint%20MLAs%E2%80%99%20team%20who%20are%20now%20holding%20up%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20for%20the%20appointment%20in%20the%20letter%20signed%20by%20six%20top%20organisational%20post%20holders%20of%20the%20BJP%20state%20unit%20including%20president%20A.%20Sharda%20Devi%20is%20significant%20considering%20Modi%20has%20not%20only%20refused%20to%20directly%20address%20the%20five-months-long%20violence%20and%20ethnic%20unrest%20in%20the%20state%20ruled%20by%20his%20party%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20affected%20people%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20for%20it%2C%20but%20has%20also%20thus%20far%20not%20given%20an%20audience%20even%20to%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20legislators%20to%20hear%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20times%20since%20the%20violence%20unfolded%20in%20the%20state%20since%20on%20May%203%2C%20MLAs%20from%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20both%20from%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20%E2%80%93%20have%20sought%20appointments%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20have%20an%20audience%20on%20the%20crisis.%20In%20June%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-narendra-modi-silence-mlas-teams%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20least%20three%20such%20delegations%20were%20camping%20in%20New%20Delhi%20seeking%20his%20time%20to%20apprise%20him%20of%20the%20unprecedented%20violence%20being%20faced%20by%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20state%2C%20leading%20to%20death%20and%20injury%20of%20several%20hundreds%20and%20loss%20of%20thousands%20of%20properties%2C%20as%20their%20elected%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-September%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%2018%20BJP%20MLAs%20from%20the%20state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2F18-manipur-mlas-camp-in-delhi-to-push-peace-efforts%2Farticleshow%2F103720528.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20been%20camping%20in%20the%20capital%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20about%20two%20weeks%20to%20meet%20various%20central%20leaders%20to%20help%20speed%20up%20the%20peace%20efforts%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20delegation%20included%20senior%20party%20leaders%20like%20Yumnam%20Khemchand%20and%20Biswajit%20Singh.%20They%20were%20keen%20to%20have%20an%20audience%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20too%20since%20there%20has%20been%20strong%20discontent%20within%20the%20public%20in%20Manipur%20for%20the%20silence%20being%20maintained%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Modi%20spoke%20only%20once%20thus%20far%20in%20reference%20to%20a%20horrific%20video%20of%20sexual%20assault%20of%20two%20women%20from%20the%20state%20by%20a%20mob%20but%20not%20without%20citing%20examples%20from%20some%20opposition%20ruled%20states%20for%20lack%20of%20safety%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20unit%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20published%20in%20various%20news%20reports%20on%20September%2030%2C%20was%20to%20seek%20Nadda%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20to%20ensure%20an%20appointment%20of%20the%20delegation%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%20A%20state%20unit%20office%20bearer%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20today%20that%20the%20delegation%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696944643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10171456%2FF8Ee91zbUAA-T1C.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-repeated-requests-pm-modi-avoids-meeting-manipur-bjp-mlas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20various%20times%20since%20the%20violence%20unfolded%20in%20the%20state%20since%20on%20May%203%2C%20MLAs%20from%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20both%20from%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20%E2%80%93%20have%20sought%20appointments%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20have%20an%20audience%20on%20the%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-repeated-requests-pm-modi-avoids-meeting-manipur-bjp-mlas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%3A%20India's%20direct%20tax%20collection%20rises%2017.95%25%20to%20Rs%2011.07%20trillion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696944521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F06%2Ffull%2F1696614521-9815.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-israel-did-not-start-this-war-but-will-finish-it-says-pm-netanyahu-123101000113_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Catch%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-israel-did-not-start-this-war-but-will-finish-it-says-pm-netanyahu-123101000113_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flive-israel-did-not-start-this-war-but-will-finish-it-says-pm-netanyahu-123101000113_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flive-israel-did-not-start-this-war-but-will-finish-it-says-pm-netanyahu-123101000113_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20Stands%20Apart%20Among%20Today's%20Young%20Politicians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F24105952%2F2022_8img22_Aug_2022_PTI08_22_2022_000199B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20A%20Delhi%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flalu-yadav-tejashwi-yadav-rabri-devi-cbi-railways-land-for-jobs%5C%22%3Egranted%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Bihar%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20his%20family%20members%20in%20the%20alleged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcbi-tejashwi-yadav-lalu-prasad-nitish-bjp-jdu-rjd-irctc%5C%22%3Eland-for-jobs%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%205.%20On%20the%20very%20same%20day%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20arrested%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fenforcement-directorate-conducts-searches-at-aap-mp-sanjay-singhs-house%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20Soon%20after%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20Tejashwi%20appeared%20before%20the%20media%20to%20condemn%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20rather%20than%20speak%20effusively%20about%20the%20bail%20and%20his%20%E2%80%98uprightness%E2%80%99%20makes%20him%20stand%20tall%20among%20the%20current%20crop%20of%20politicians%20for%20whom%20politics%20is%20all%20about%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20torturing%20all%20regional%20parties%20which%20are%20doing%20good%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20extending%20solidarity%20to%20AAP%2C%20which%20is%20in%20crisis%20as%20three%20of%20its%20top%20leaders%20are%20currently%20imprisoned.%20%E2%80%9CI%20condemn%20the%20arrest%20of%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20The%20BJP%20is%20harassing%20the%20parties%20which%20are%20addressing%20the%20issues%20concerning%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-rise-of-tejashwi-yadav-signals-significant-change-in-bihar-politics%5C%22%3EThe%20Rise%20of%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20Signals%20Significant%20Change%20in%20Bihar%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20frightened%20more%20at%20the%20release%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20report%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Bihar%20government%20giving%20employment%20in%20lakhs%20to%20the%20youths.%20They%20(the%20BJP)%20are%20incapable%20of%20fighting%20a%20political%20battle.%20The%20only%20recourse%20they%20know%20is%20to%20misuse%20the%20central%20agencies%20against%20its%20opponents.%20But%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20fear.%20These%20diabolical%20moves%20will%20strengthen%20our%20resolve%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20up%20on%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20statements%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20MP%20and%20spokesperson%20Manoj%20Jha%20personally%20visited%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%20to%20extend%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20support.%20Although%20other%20constituent%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20condemned%20the%20arrest%20of%20Singh%2C%20it%20was%20only%20the%20RJD%20which%20went%20a%20step%20further%20to%20send%20its%20representative%20to%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3ERJD-AAP%20relationship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20onslaught%20on%20AAP%20is%20sharply%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20cold%20relationship%20that%20his%20father%20and%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20are%20known%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELalu%20Yadav%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20AAP%20since%20the%20period%20it%20emerged%20from%20the%20Anna%20Hazare-led%20movement%20against%20corruption%20in%202014.%20Lalu%20has%20differences%20with%20Kejriwal%20and%20AAP%20for%20he%20perceives%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-Mandal%E2%80%9D%20and%20inimical%20to%20the%20battle%20for%20social%20justice.%20He%20also%20suspects%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20Sangh%3Cem%3E%20parivar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20philosophy%20which%20the%20former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20detests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20and%20most%20of%20his%20party%20men%2C%20including%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20were%20very%20critical%20of%20Lalu%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption.%20They%20perceived%20that%20their%20association%20with%20the%20RJD%20in%20any%20manner%20would%20cost%20their%20credentials%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-corruption%E2%80%99%20crusaders%20%E2%80%93%20the%20plank%20on%20which%20it%20emerged%20on%20the%20political%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20when%20Lalu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-news-india%2Fwhy-the-lalu-kejriwal-hug-became-a-controversy%2F%5C%22%3Ehugged%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kejriwal%20at%20a%20meeting%20(of%20Mahagathbandhan)%2C%20Kejriwal%20said%20openly%20that%20he%20did%20not%20like%20it.%20Lalu%20then%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccourtesy%20of%20%5Ba%5D%20public%20stage%E2%80%9D%20while%20clarifying%20that%20there%20was%20no%20change%20of%20heart%20on%20his%20part%20in%20the%20way%20he%20viewed%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20Photos%3A%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20(Government%20of%20India%2FGODL%20License)%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20(Government%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%2FGODL%20License)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20Kejriwal%20and%20AAP%20is%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20that%20of%20his%20father.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20Kejriwal%20will%20rethink%20his%20and%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20the%20RJD%2C%20particularly%20after%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20public%20show%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20appears%20to%20have%20brought%20the%20RJD%20and%20AAP%20closer%20are%20the%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20%E2%80%93%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20%E2%80%93%20framing%20their%20leaders%20in%20corruption%20cases.%20Both%20parties%20say%20the%20cases%20represent%20a%20misuse%20of%20central%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20one%20day%20after%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20granted%20bail%20to%20Tejashwi%20and%20the%20CBI%20arrested%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20questioned%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%E2%80%99s%20charges%20against%20another%20AAP%20leader%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%20Manish%20Sisodia%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-money-has-come-to-manish-sisodia-how-will-you-bring-him-under-pmla-sc-to-ed%5C%22%3Estrong%20words%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20is%20the%20proof%3F%20Where%20is%20the%20evidence%3F%20Except%20for%20the%20statement%20of%20Dinesh%20Arora%20(a%20businessman)%2C%20is%20there%20any%20other%20evidence%3F%20How%20will%20you%20bring%20Manish%20Sisodia%20under%20the%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20top%20court%20said%20whilst%20hearing%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20observation%20has%20created%20doubts%20about%20actions%20against%20the%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20two%20central%20agencies%20have%20implicated%20Tejashwi%20in%20the%20land-for-job%20case%20is%20hardly%20convincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%2C%20some%20candidates%20obtained%20jobs%20in%20the%20railways%20in%20lieu%20of%20plots%20of%20land%20that%20they%20gave%20to%20Lalu%20when%20the%20latter%20was%20the%20minister%20for%20railways%20(2004-09).%20Tejashwi%20was%20a%20minor%20at%20that%20time%2C%20playing%20cricket%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Cricket%20Control%20of%20India%20(BCCI)%E2%80%99s%20Under-15%20team%20and%20living%20away%20from%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20CBI%20itself%20dropped%20these%20allegations%20in%202011%20after%20it%20had%20said%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20to%20carry%20them%20forward.%20But%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%20suddenly%20raided%20establishments%20connected%20to%20Lalu%20in%20Patna%20and%20Delhi%20in%202017%2C%20when%20Tejashwi%20was%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20first%20Mahagathbandhan%20government%2C%20reopening%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcbi-tejashwi-yadav-lalu-prasad-nitish-bjp-jdu-rjd-irctc%5C%22%3ESo%20Why%20Is%20the%20CBI%20After%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20Now%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20fell%20silent%20again%20for%20five%20years%20after%20Nitish%20broke%20away%20from%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20and%20rejoined%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20they%20carried%20out%20raids%20on%20Lalu%20and%20his%20family%20members%20after%20Nitish%20returned%20to%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20again%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntriguingly%2C%20Tejashwi%20didn%E2%80%99t%20figure%20in%20the%20original%20chargesheet%20of%20the%20land-for-jobs%20scam%20case.%20But%20the%20CBI%20named%20him%20in%20the%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20filed%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20attributes%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%20broadly%20appears%20to%20have%20three%20special%20attributes%20that%20contrast%20him%20with%20other%20young%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20his%20complete%20focus%20on%20the%20issues%20concerning%20the%20people.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20he%20was%20fighting%20a%20lonely%20battle%20against%20the%20BJP-Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20with%20his%20father%20in%20jail%2C%20Tejashwi%20promised%2010%2C00%2C000%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20if%20his%20party%20was%20elected%20to%20power.%20He%20based%20his%20campaign%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20employment%20and%20outsmarted%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20who%20addressed%20as%20many%20as%2031%20election%20rallies%20in%20Bihar%20at%20that%20time.%20Even%20though%20the%20RJD%20was%20unable%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%20it%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20with%2078%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F596103-lalu-tejaswi-pti.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%2FFiles%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-175013%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%2FFiles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20deputy%20CM%2C%20he%20has%20shown%20that%20he%20can%20implement%20what%20he%20promised.%20The%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20has%20already%20given%20over%20two%20lakh%20jobs%20since%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20government%20was%20formed%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20Bihar%20is%20said%20to%20be%20far%20ahead%20of%20others%20in%20providing%20employment%20to%20the%20youth%2C%20whereas%20Modi%20and%20his%20Union%20government%20have%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20he%20had%20joined%20hands%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20caste-based%20census%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20opposition.%20Now%2C%20Bihar%20is%20the%20first%20state%20to%20have%20come%20out%20with%20the%20caste%20survey%20report%2C%20giving%20strength%20to%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20the%20young%20Tejashwi%20is%20quite%20sharp%20in%20identifying%20the%20issues%20that%20would%20succeed%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20gargantuan%20election%20machine.%20Secondly%2C%20he%20is%20bold%2C%20a%20trait%20that%20he%20has%20inherited%20from%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20personally%20went%20to%20express%20support%20to%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20during%20the%202021%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20Modi%20had%20mocked%20Mamata%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDidi-o-Didi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20were%20after%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamata%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20his%20support%20at%20the%20time%20when%20political%20leaders%20from%20other%20parties%20acted%20diplomatically%20to%20avoid%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98wrath%E2%80%99.%20As%20a%20railway%20minister%2C%20she%20had%20tabled%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Ffocus%2Fstory%2Flalu-vs-mamata-whos-right-17676-2010-01-11%5C%22%3EWhite%20Paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20But%20when%20she%20came%20to%20attend%20the%20first%20conclave%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20in%20August%2C%20she%20bowed%20down%20before%20Lalu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20third%20but%20equally%20important%20attribute%20is%20deference%20to%20elders.%20He%20has%20the%20utmost%20respect%20for%20Nitish%2C%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20contemporary%2C%20and%20avoids%20speaking%20when%20he%20is%20with%20the%20chief%20minister.%20He%20touches%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20feet%20whenever%20he%20goes%20out%20of%20home%20and%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696943735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F24105952%2F2022_8img22_Aug_2022_PTI08_22_2022_000199B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yadav-stands-apart-today-young-politicians%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20has%20already%20proved%20his%20mettle%20in%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP.%20He%20is%20poised%20for%20bigger%20things%20given%20his%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20masses%20that%20few%20other%20leaders%20of%20his%20age%20can%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A123%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yadav-stands-apart-today-young-politicians%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prakash%20Chhabria-led%20Orbit%20moves%20SC%20over%20Finolex%20Cables%20non-disclosure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696943281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-04%2F20%2Ffull%2F1555784554-4145.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fprakash-chhabria-led-orbit-moves-sc-over-finolex-cables-non-disclosure-123101001001_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cousins%20Prakash%20and%20Chhabria%20have%20been%20at%20odds%20over%20gaining%20control%20of%20Finolex%20Cables%2C%20a%20%242-billion%20pipe%20and%20cable%20manufacturer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fprakash-chhabria-led-orbit-moves-sc-over-finolex-cables-non-disclosure-123101001001_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fprakash-chhabria-led-orbit-moves-sc-over-finolex-cables-non-disclosure-1