e%20finds%20very%20cathartic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGardening%20gives%20me%20mental%20satisfaction%20and%20is%20relaxing.%20I%20never%20get%20bored.%20Every%20morning%2C%20when%20I%20go%20upstairs%2C%20I%20find%20something%20new.%20I%20see%20parrots%20and%20sparrows%20chirping%2C%20and%20find%20some%20new%20flowers%20on%20my%20cactus.%20I%20find%20squirrels%20roaming%20around.%20My%20mother%2C%20father%2C%20wife%20and%20daughter%20help%20me%20water%20the%20plants%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20for%20us%20to%20spend%20time%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Navdeep%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dentist%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20gardening%20was%20ignited%20by%20his%20father%2C%20who%20himself%20is%20a%20plant-lover.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20grew%20a%20small%20garden%20in%20our%20house.%20As%20a%20young%20child%2C%20I%20saw%20him%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20tending%20the%20garden.%20He%20just%20loved%20plants%20and%20that%20has%20rubbed%20off%20on%20me.%20We%20had%20so%20many%20beautiful%20flowers.%20About%2010%20years%20back%2C%20the%20garden%20had%20to%20be%20filled%20in%20to%20make%20space%20for%20my%20older%20brother%E2%80%99s%20car%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20oasis%20of%20calm%20in%20a%20busy%20city%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-22.55.16-1-1696861962.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Navdeep's%20terrace%20garden.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-22.55.16-1-1696861962.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-2