tance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMuscular%20Dystrophy%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SMA%20is%20caused%20by%20missing%20or%20mutated%20SMN1%20or%20SMN2%20genes%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20survival%20muscle%20neuron%20genes.%20The%20protein%20produced%20by%20this%20gene%20%E2%80%94%20SMN%20protein%20%E2%80%94%20facilitates%20movement%20and%20is%20needed%20by%20motor%20neurons%20to%20function%20effectively.%20Since%20the%20gene%20is%20faulty%20or%20missing%2C%20it%20impedes%20movement%20among%20those%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20SMA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindividuals%20experience%20several%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20voluntary%20movements%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20the%20head%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20limbs.%20Priya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20spinal%20cord%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20are%20affected%2C%20people%20with%20SMA%20also%20develop%20scoliosis%20or%20spinal%20curvature.%20I%20have%20it%20too%20and%20I%20manage%20it%20by%20stuffing%20a%20lot%20of%20cushions%20around%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20limited%20mobility%2C%20I%20have%20low%20muscle%20tone%20which%20results%20in%20weaker%20bone%20health%20and%20density.%20Even%20lifting%20a%20book%20seems%20like%20a%20Herculean%20task%20to%20me.%20My%20condition%20also%20makes%20me%20prone%20to%20frequent%20fractures%20and%20joint%20dislocations.%20Since%20my%20mobility%20is%20impacted%2C%20I%20use%20a%20wheelchair%20to%20move%20around%20and%20need%20support%20with%20activities%20of%20daily%20living.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20Priya%2C%20many%20others%20with%20SMA%20require%20wheelchairs%20too.%20They%20may%20also%20rely%20on%20different%20support%20needs%20for%20daily%20life.%20Some%20patients%20have%20difficulty%20in%20swallowing%20and%20eating%20food%20and%20may%20require%20a%20feeding%20tube%20while%20others%20with%20compromised%20lungs%20may%20need%20breathing%20support%20or%20ventilation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-300x175.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-500x292.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-768x448.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-150x88.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331662%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Priya%2C%20her%20caregiver%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20my%20parents%20have%20aged%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20them%20to%20lift%20me%20up%2C%20carry%20me%20around%20or%20support%20my%20needs.%20If%20my%20caregiver%20goes%20on%20a%20leave%20for%20even%20one%20day%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20my%20mother%20and%20even%20the%20most%20basic%20of%20everyday%20activities%20seem%20impossible.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20recounts%20how%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20people%20give%20unsolicited%20advice%20to%20her%20and%20her%20family%20about%20managing%20her%20disability%20without%20realising%20none%20of%20them%20work%20because%20her%20body%20functions%20differently%20than%20other%20people%E2%80%99s.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20while