y%20demonstrated%20that%20students%20and%20young%20people%20can%20use%20their%20education%20to%20make%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20project%20received%20recognition%20at%20the%20Youth%20for%20Earth%20Campaign%202023%20%E2%80%94%20a%20platform%20for%20young%20changemakers%20to%20showcase%20their%20innovations.%20Conducted%20by%20Mobius%20Foundation%20in%20partnership%20with%20The%20Climate%20Project%20Foundation%2C%20200%20youth%20groups%20participated%20in%20this%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETen%20of%20the%20best%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20made%20on%20the%20theme%20%E2%80%98United%20Nations%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goal%2013%3A%20Climate%20Action%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20were%20rewarded%20at%20the%20fifth%20International%20Conference%20on%20Sustainability%20Education%20(ICSE).%20Five%20of%20these%20were%20awarded%20in%20the%20youth%20category%20(schools)%20and%20five%20in%20the%20senior%20category%2C%20which%20included%20colleges%2C%20universities%20and%20independent%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProject%20BacWP%20won%20the%20second%20prize%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20in%20the%20youth%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202274px)%20100vw%2C%202274px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dignitaries%20at%20the%205th%20International%20Conference%20on%20Sustainability%20Education%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492.jpg%202274w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492-768x511.jpg%2